OL,5,     GMotoring magazine. Jeremy,
OL,6,     GRichard and James are challenged
OL,7,     Gto each drive a second-hand car
OL,8,     Gacross the wilds of Botswana,
OL,9,     Gfacing obstacles such as salt
OL,10,     Gpans, rivers and animals.
OL,11,G2215FTop Gear: Africa Special Part 1
OL,12,     GIn the first of a two-part Top
OL,13,     GGear special, Jeremy Clarkson,
OL,14,     GRichard Hammond and James May are
OL,15,     Gin Africa with a simple mission -
OL,16,     Gto find the definitive source of
OL,17,     Gthe Nile.
OL,18,G2315FTop Gear: Africa Special Part 2
OL,19,     GThe trio endures traffic,
OL,20,     Gmudslides, and navigation
OL,21,     Gchallenges to find the Nile's
OL,22,     Gsource.
